{
  "_doc": "The command + tool REGISTRY — all registry DATA as data. Loaded by command_catalog.py (which holds only the loader, derived views, and drift asserts). commands = user-facing help entries; category_order = help grouping; tools = tool FACTS (req/vm/effect/rev — effect is an array, restored to a tuple on load; null = read-only); tool_name_arg = which arg names a tool's target VM (default 'name'); tool_triggers = per-tool intent words for the context-assistant; post_create_attach = create->attach hints. A tool's RISK/gating is NOT here — that's a per-contract judgment in the .grgn agent files.",
